hi deepseek.... how are you doing today.. i need help on building a site, i want to build a microfinance site. give my site a company logo and name with a multiple section menu make my menu drop down (items linking the user to the different pages of the website) make the menu and footer sticky.. do not load everything in one / single prompt and section but section each section separate . add  comments to the code. use tailwind css . make is unique and professional. without javascript


use HTML, Tailwind CSS, and responsive design with no Javascript, a professional structure that will look modern and meet most assignment requirements.

Project Name

TravelbyNeche Adventures

Color Palette

* Primary: #0F766E (Teal)
* Secondary: #F59E0B (Amber)
* Accent: #2563EB (Blue)
* Background: #F8FAFC
* Text: #1F2937

This combination gives a vibrant travel feel.

