Tailwind Features to Include

* Responsive navigation with a hamburger menu on mobile
* Dropdown menus for every main navigation item
* Sticky navigation (sticky top-0)
* Sticky footer (or a footer that stays at the bottom using a flex layout)
* Hero section with an overlay
* CSS Grid for destination and package cards
* Hover animations (hover:scale-105, transition)
* Rounded cards and subtle shadows
* Gradient buttons
* Smooth scrolling
* Responsive layouts for mobile, tablet, and desktop